    "longBusinessSummary": "Song Ba Joint Stock Company invests in the construction of hydropower projects in Vietnam. It produces and trades in electricity; and provides consultancy services for investment project construction, survey, and design construction of hydroelectric projects with a capacity of approximately 30 MW, as well as power lines and substations of approximately 110 KV. In addition, the company offers consulting services for construction supervision and project management of small and medium hydropower projects, power lines and, substations of approximately 110 KV; vocational training services, including management and operation of hydropower plants; consultancy services on environmental solutions and resettlement; and repair and maintenance services for hydropower plants. Further, it supervises the construction of irrigation and hydropower works; installs equipment for construction works; research and manufacture mechanical and electrical parts of hydroelectric power plants; and trading in real estate. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Da Nang, Vietnam.",
